tion: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">- Độ d&agrave;i d&acirc;y c&aacute;p: 2,1 m</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">C&Aacute;C T&Iacute;NH NĂNG KH&Aacute;C</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">- Chiếu s&aacute;ng RGB LIGHTSYNC1Y&ecirc;u cầu phần mềm HUB G của Logitech</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">- Tay cầm b&ecirc;n bằng cao su được đ&uacute;c phun</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">- 6 n&uacute;t c&oacute; thể lập tr&igrave;nh</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; word-break: break-word; color: #333333; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;